title: Return fire 1 with music (and without CD)
description:
This is a very old game the I was playing on a 133Mhz so it would work on your pc ;)
To launch the game, use install.reg, then go to the properties of the RFIRE.EXE and put compatibility win 98, 256 colors and 640x480. Just launch RFIRE.EXE to play. enjoy !

all the musics of the game are in score.wav (for thoes who have the game without music)


Game desc :
This is a game where it fits in all the genres of Strategy, Action. You can take control of one of 4 veichles, a jeep, helicopter, tank and a missle launching vehicle (but actually called The Armoured Support Vehicle (ASV)). While there are 2 ways to win, the easier one would be to capture the enemy&#039;s flag by bringing it to your bunker with the frail Jeep. And that is the main objective. The other way to win is to destroy your enemy. A secondary objective
